{"title":"怒潮澎湃——反对美国的军事挑衅","authors":["沙鸥"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒潮澎湃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——反对美国的军事挑衅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗万杆迎风吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前汇洪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民被激怒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧捏成一拳头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道铜墙厚千丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕狂风和恶浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝胆敢用头撞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自掘坟墓把身葬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们行使主权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国说是“扩张”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们处理内政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国说是“侵略”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我国神圣的内海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国说是它的“边防”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国一手举着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的字典，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手向我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥刀弄枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒潮滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云天拍浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民动员起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三山五岳把路让！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争威胁能吓谁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾一定要解放！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}